rows.label: qst702607_msg0001
rows.name:
Dudan salvaged the great
gold-collecting machine for me.

rows.label: qst702607_msg0002
rows.name:
It looked just like the
gold-collecting machine I read
about in a book when I was little.

rows.label: qst702607_msg0003
rows.name:
I thought it was a sign
from the heavens.

rows.label: qst702607_msg0004
rows.name:
Dudan did his best, but he's
not an expert, so this is
as far as he can go...

rows.label: qst702607_msg0005
rows.name:
Could you ask someone who knows about
machines to modify it further?

rows.label: qst702607_msg0006
rows.name:
I've come this far... I absolutely
want to get that gold.

rows.label: qst702607_msg0101
rows.name:
It collected something!
It collected something!

rows.label: qst702607_msg0102
rows.name:
I want to believe it's gold, but I
don't know what it collected yet...
